A2: (for x being (Element of V) holds ( a . x ) = ( ( f . x ) + ( g . x ) ))
and
A3: (for x being (Element of V) holds ( b . x ) = ( ( f . x ) + ( g . x ) ));
now
let x being (Element of V);
thus ( a . x ) = ( ( f . x ) + ( g . x ) ) by A2
.= ( b . x ) by A3;
